messages.content: Vulpe is pacing around in her room. Its the big day.  Shes getting  married. Shes so  nervous! She glances at her dress. She cant put it in yet, hair and makeup  should probably  be first. She pulls out her Tesseract  to text Sanguis
She shifts back into her mun form and sits on her bed.
((shall I yeet radium in
(Ye
The wall opened up, and radium walked in, very tired and holding a robotic leg "Hey"
The kistune was startled by her sudden appearance "U-Uhm- Hi. You.....know you could of used the door right???"
"Ah. didn't want others to see me." she shrugged
"Alright...." She looked over at the leg she was holding
"Lay on the bed, I'll put it on, it's gonna hurt like a bitch " she warned, making her supplies float on a rock to her
She nodded and laid down on the bed
Radium carefully implimented the leg, it was *painful* but quite short
She bit her lip to stop herself from making any noise
"aaaaand done !" she tiredly clapped her hands

She sat up and flex it a bit before standing up and testing out her new leg. She smiled brightly, tears starting to fall "Thank you....Now...I can walk again...Ill be able to walk down the isle!!! If theres anything I can do as repayment let me know....."
She shook her head "nah, it's fine." she sat on the floor " I'm just so *tired*"
"You should get some rest then..."

"Since I'm done making this dude's torso and your leg I *finally* can. yeah." she yawned
"anyway, have a fantastic day"
"Thank you again Radium....I hope you get some sleep..." She smiled a bit
She waved, giving a tired smile "still didn't beat my own all nighter high score so I'll be good"
"Alright i'm gonna head out " she got on a roc and left, closing the walls behind her
Vulpe waves. Shes in a really good mood
Opal knocked on the door
Vulpe walked over and opened the door
Opal waved "Vulpe ! ready for your-" she cuts herself off as she noticed her new leg "Oh! Congratulations! you inally got it!"
She nodded excitedly "Yeah!!! Im ready." Her tails are still wagging
"Let's get you all dressed up then!" she steped in
She nodded again. Shes nervous but also excited
"Alright! so, the dress-" she looked around
It was hanging up in her closet
She took it out o the closet "oh! what a pretty dress you have!"
"Dominus made it for me...." She smiled
Eventually she was all ready. She was staring at herself in the mirror. She looked amazing....
"So, satisfied ?" Opal hummed
She nodded "I look so pretty..."
She giggled "Now go ! Enjoy your wedding my dear !"
"Well I gotta wait for everyone to be at the alter and stuff first...." She chuckled "Gotta wait here till Veteris says everythings ready. I dont want Puppy seeing me early...Wanna suprise him."
Her tails are wagging quite a bit now.

Meriad knocks on Vulpes door

Vulpe opens it and waves, shes got her mask on. Its clear shes nervous

"Wow!! You look ama- OH!!!!! You got your new leg!!! Im so happy for you!!" She smiled

"Ye-yeah..." She pulled her dress up a bit and flexed her new leg "Its nice to be able to walk again...."
@◎☆E☆◎ (incase u wanna gave Dominus say anything
“Oh so look so cute!”
Her tauls wagged even more "My tails wont stop wagging....." She giggled
"All right all thats left is to check on Veteris then I think we should be able to start the wedding!!" Meriad hummed
Several knocks gently pound against the door, “You ready?” Veteris, called
Vulpe got up and open the door, tails wagging even more still "Yeah..!!! I am!" She smiled
He held out his hand, “alright then.”
She took it, ready to walk down the isle
He silently walks her down the hall.
Vulpe pulled Sanguis here and flopped onto the bed
He snuggled closer to her, sighing, “so warm...”
She purred loudly, tails wagging a bjt
Shes very happy
Eventually the kitsune falls asleep
A nightmare startles her awake. She looks over at her sleeping husband with a smile. She gently kissed his forehead and gets up to change out of her wedding dress and into something more casual

She stares at her new metal leg in the mirror with a small smile. Sure its not fluffy and normal but she doesn't care. She can walk again! She flexed it a bit, moving it around sseeing just how far her range of motion with it is. Shes happy. Thats all that matters to her. She looks at her hair and undoes it from the current style, shaking it out before grabbing a brush and brushing it. She should probably brush her tails too....
She sits on the bed and begins to brush her tails
After shes done she lays back down and cuddles up to Sanguis again
....her stomach growls. "Ah...." She sits up again
She sighs and gently kisses Sanguis' head "Ill be back in a bit Puppy..." she whispers
She gets off the bed and throws on something before walking out
Vulpe is back and climbs back into bed, happily snuggling up to him
"I love you so much...." She whispered
She had fallen asleep again but soon woke up with her leg in pain. She didnt want to wake Sanguis so she tried to ignore it
“Darling?” He tiredly mumbled, rubbing his eyes
"A-Ah- Puppy- Did I wa-wake you....?" She smiled at him, trying to hide that she was in pain
“Mhm, not really.” He yawned, “Are you,...alright.”
"....Its....my leg...." She sighed "Its hurting fo-for some reason...."
“Ah, probably still aching from the replacement, I can...get you some pain relievers from the bath cabbiet.”
She nodded a bit "Th-thank you Puppy...."
“Right, be back soon kitten.” Sanguis gently kisses his wife’s forehead before getting out of the bed and room.
Her tails wagged a bit at the kiss
Thr pain wasnt stopping...She laid on the bed, holding her leg in pain. It hurt so much...

The door creaked back open as the mun returned with two pills and a glass of water
“Hopefully this will help a little”
She sat back up "Th-Thanks...." She took the pills and water from him. ".....I......have never taken pills before......." Shes a bit embarrassed
Shes not sure how to take them
“Take one at a time, place it in your mouth and use the water to swallow it down.” He points

She nodded and did so. After she had taken them she looked at Sanguis "I.....have a question....When we where fused....Vulguis went feral....Did....you feel it too...? The rage that make them go feral....?" She rubbed her arm a bit, unsure on how to exactly word it
“.......yeah, it was...*intense*.” Sanguis sighed
"Ah...Im....sorry about that....." She played with her tails
“No, I was also just as tempted to hit that bastard as well..”
"I feel kinda bad about slashing his eye like that....But...I liked it when we fused....I felt even closer to you then before..." She purred, hugging him a bit
“I did too, it felt...great.” He snuggled close
She purred more, nuzzling him a bit "Mm...I love looking at you....You're so handsome....And when you hold me close I like it....I just love being in your arms...." She smiled, kissing his cheek
The kitsune decided to be a little cheeky and moved down to kiss his neck
He let out a small squeak, “ah why you-“ for payback, he planted a kiss on her ear
She blushed madly, letting out a small squeak  her ear twitching
She huffs and kisses his neck again, moving a bit lower this time
"I love you so much puppy...." she grinned and decided to leave a mark on his neck
“Mmm I love you too...kitten...” he purrs, burying his head into her hair.
She holds him close, purring happily
She closes her eyes, ready to fall asleep again
Shes awake again and she can smell Mamizous scent. She growls a bit "Why is she here."
She gets out of the bed and follows the scent

Vulpe pushes open the door and lets Mamizou off her back

The tanuki sits silently on the bed, very nervous

"Puppy? Are you awake??" Vulpe asked

@◎☆E☆◎

"Hes probably still sleeping....." she went through her dresser and pulled out a shirt and a skirt that should fit Mamizou "Here. Get changed." She pointed to a folding screen she had that would concel the tanuki 

Mamizou nodded and went to change

She came back out when she changed 

"Ok...Now ill get some bandages and clean you up ok? Stay here. If Puppy wakes up before I come back tell him Ill explain everything." Vulpe hummed
The kitsune left to get stuff to help Mamizou

The absence of a dent in the bed cause Sanguis to stir 
“Hmm....?”
Mamizou froze up. Uh oh. She had really been hoping he wouldn't wake up till Vulpe came back

He groggily uses his arms to hoist himself up, rubbing his eyes 
“Hmph......Kitt...en...?”
The mun can’t really recognize the silhouette
"...U-Uh-" She clamps a hand over her mouth. Her voice is a dead giveaway of who she is

The voice send shocks of anger, now fully awake 
“**You**”
He launched himself near her, pinning the mun to the ground
“**What did you do to my kitten?!?**”

"I DIDNT DO ANYTHING I SWEAR! IM NOT HERE TO CAUSE TROUBLE! SH-SHE WENT TO GET STUFF TO CLEAN MY WOUNDS-" She whimpered, shaking "I ca-came here seeking help! Vu-vulpe told me she would tell you everything but y-you need to know- Radium had kidnapped me. Sh-she cut my tail off....dissected me alive....."
She sounds absolutely terrified

He snarls, but Radiums name seems to divert his anger
“You’re lucky I hate Radium more then you...” ge slightly releases his hold

She scampers away from him and to a corner of the room

Vulpe comes back with bandages and some other stuff. "Oh Puppy! You're awake!" She walks over to Mamizou "Ok Mamizou this might sting but we need to make sure these dont get infected."

She began to clean the wounds and wrapped them with bandages. "There....You should try and avoid moving alot." She picked her up and put her on the bed "Stay here for now...Ill ask Dominus if there's another spare room you can sleep in..."
Mamizou brings her knees up to her chest, she really wishes she still had her tail
